{"tid":1196460,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"椎間盤突出，求介紹醫生/治療","createTime":"2019-06-09T19:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T20:44:22.000Z","uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31601957daa7333116222f107476ccc31e14ccbb","tid":1196460,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:54:32.000Z","msg":"爸爸好幾年前已有椎間盤問題，一直都有睇跌打控制<br />\n到呢幾個月返新工，需要搬野同郁動得多啲<br />\n佢既病情嚴重咗好多，需要拐杖助行<br />\n<br />\n呢兩星期突然急轉直下，痛到日日睇跌打、搵針灸、推拿、睇中醫都幫助不大，之前食既止痛藥都冇太大效用，骨頭都不斷發出咯咯聲<br />\n<br />\n各位有冇經驗分享，或可以推介醫治椎間盤問題既醫生幫幫手？見到佢痛到咁，真係好心痛。爸爸先得五十幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9af8210603bdebadfdbe1f476ee50650c2e114","tid":1196460,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:57:59.000Z","msg":"窮就去公醫排期做手術<br />\n應該要排9個月到1年<br />\n做完休息3個月到半年就會好番"},{"pid":"e8906a9a5496bc81353ac6e5cf806c362044196e","tid":1196460,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b9af8210603bdebadfdbe1f476ee50650c2e114","tid":1196460,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:57:59.000Z","msg":"窮就去公醫排期做手術<br />\n應該要排9個月到1年<br />\n做完休息3個月到半年就會好番"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:18:30.000Z","msg":"做手術有風險，好驚萬一失敗行唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683e2ec81cdeed0af8b296bd7836ff24dc96c5e0","tid":1196460,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e8906a9a5496bc81353ac6e5cf806c362044196e","tid":1196460,"uid":118041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b9af8210603bdebadfdbe1f476ee50650c2e114","tid":1196460,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T19:57:59.000Z","msg":"窮就去公醫排期做手術<br />\n應該要排9個月到1年<br />\n做完休息3個月到半年就會好番"},"citedBy":1,"replyT